short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Extension is used To Calculate Exam Total Percentage

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you need to calculate your exam percentage? You can do it in a matter of seconds with this app! Simply enter the number of questions you answered correctly and the number of questions you answered incorrectly and it will give you your percentage. The percentage calculator also includes a graph to help you visualize your progress over time. The graph also includes a trend line to help you make a prediction of your score. You can also save your data to see how you are doing over time.
